<p style="text-align: center;"><strong><span style="font-size: 16px;">能带多少？</span></strong></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><strong><span style="font-size: 16px;">今天</span></strong></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><strong><span style="font-size: 16px;">福网君今天就来给大家支招</span></strong><span style="font-size: 16px;"></span></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span><strong>怎么把铁路限带品全部带回家</strong></span></span></p>
<p><span style="font-size: 16px;"><strong>限量携带物品</strong></span></p>
<p style="text-align: justify;"><span>1.不超过</span><span><strong>20ml</strong></span><span>的指甲油、去光剂、染发剂。</span></p>
<p style="text-align: justify;"><span>2.不超过</span><strong><span>120ml</span></strong><span>的冷烫精、摩丝、发胶、杀虫剂、空气清新剂等自喷压力容器。</span></p>
<p style="text-align: justify;"><span>3.安全火柴2小盒</span><span></span><span>。</span></p>
<p style="text-align: justify;"><span>4.普通打火机2个。</span></p>
<p><span style="font-size: 16px;"><strong>限带品怎么带回家？</strong></span></p>
<p style="text-align: justify;"><span>为解决旅客部分物品</span><span>无法通过安检的不便，</span><span>福州、福州南站近日在各安检口</span><span>处置台旁边安装了18台</span><strong><span>限带品自助处置柜</span></strong><span>，</span><span>只需要5步，就能把限带物品寄回家。</span></p>
